room_title: Escape room "Houdini’s Book Of Secrets" by Escape Medina in Akron
room_description: Houdini had to leave town in a hurry & needs your help! A band of thieves are on their way to steal his most prized possession, his book of secrets which contains his life‘s work. Can you find the clues Mr. Houdini left for you in his office and save the book before the deadly thieves get there?
